---
import { endangeredStats } from '../data/content';
---

<!-- wave from Tips (#1a4a2e) into conservation (#060f09) -->
<div class="wave-sep" aria-hidden="true">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 80" preserveAspectRatio="none"><path d="M0,60 C360,80 1080,20 1440,50 L1440,80 L0,80Z" fill="#060f09"/></svg>
</div>

<section id="conservation" class="section-conservation">
  <div class="cons-orb" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="section-inner">

    <div class="cons-header reveal">
      <p class="section-label">Conservación</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">El reino en peligro</h2>
      <p class="cons-intro">
        Cada día desaparecen especies que tardaron millones de años en
        evolucionar. Lo que perdemos no es solo diversidad botánica —
        perdemos los cimientos invisibles de los ecosistemas que nos sostienen.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="endangered-grid">
      {endangeredStats.map((s, i) => (
        <div class="endangered-item reveal" style={`--delay:${i * 0.12}s`}>
          <div class="endangered-number">{s.number}</div>
          <p class="endangered-label">{s.label}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="cons-body reveal">
      <p>
        La pérdida de una planta no es un dato aislado. Es la extinción
        simultánea de los insectos que la polinizaban, los hongos que la
        alimentaban y las aves que dispersaban sus semillas. La naturaleza
        no conoce las extinciones en singular.
      </p>
      <p>
        La buena noticia: cada persona que cultiva, que cuida, que aprende
        a respetar el ciclo vegetal contribuye activamente a la preservación.
        No necesitas un laboratorio para proteger la vida.
      </p>
      <a href="#tips" class="cons-cta">
        Aprende a cultivar
        <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- wave into Footer (#0d2b1a) -->
<div class="wave-sep" aria-hidden="true">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 80" preserveAspectRatio="none"><path d="M0,30 C480,80 960,0 1440,60 L1440,80 L0,80Z" fill="#0d2b1a"/></svg>
</div>

<style>
  .section-conservation {
    background: #060f09;
    color: var(--c-text);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cons-orb {
    position: absolute;
    width: 600px;
    height: 600px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(45,122,79,.12), transparent 70%);
    top: -200px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .section-conservation .section-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 5rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .cons-header { max-width: 680px; }

  .cons-intro {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--c-muted);
    line-height: var(--lh-loose);
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .endangered-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: rgba(126,200,160,.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .endangered-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  .endangered-item {
    background: #060f09;
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: background var(--transition-base);
  }
  .endangered-item:hover { background: rgba(126,200,160,.04); }

  .endangered-number {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: .7rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--c-cream), rgba(126,200,160,.7));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .endangered-label {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--c-muted);
    line-height: var(--lh-base);
    max-width: 180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cons-body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem 4rem;
    align-items: end;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cons-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  .cons-body p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--c-muted);
    line-height: var(--lh-loose);
  }

  .cons-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: .5rem;
    padding: .85rem 1.8rem;
    border: var(--border-medium);
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    color: var(--c-light);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    letter-spacing: .05em;
    transition: background var(--transition-base), color var(--transition-base);
    width: fit-content;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
  .cons-cta svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; transition: transform var(--transition-base); }
  .cons-cta:hover { background: var(--c-light); color: var(--c-deep); }
  .cons-cta:hover svg { transform: translateX(4px); }
</style>

<script>
  import { inView, animate } from 'motion';

  document.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('.endangered-item').forEach((el, i) => {
    inView(el, () => {
      animate(
        el,
        { opacity: [0, 1], transform: ['translateY(20px)', 'translateY(0)'] },
        { duration: 0.6, delay: i * 0.12, easing: [0.16, 1, 0.3, 1] }
      );
    }, { margin: '-10% 0px' });
  });
</script>
